0. Please execute

     `./init.sh`

   to get jfbterm's source code.

1. To compile jfbtermï¼Œplease execute
   
     `cd jfbterm-0.4.7/`
     `LDFLAGS="-L/usr/lib/" ./configure --prefix=/usr/` 
     `make`

   P.S. /usr/ can be set to your prefered path.
   P.S. LDFLAGS is needed to locate where libucimf.so is.

2. To install, please execute
      
     `make install`

